{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1623940/extras/eMBARK.png?t=1730299925\" />Bramble The Mountain King takes you on a gripping and unsettling journey through stunning environments. Take on the role of Olle, a young boy setting off to rescue his sister, kidnapped by a dreaded troll.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1623940/extras/troll_1.gif?t=1730299925\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1623940/extras/sTEP.png?t=1730299925\" />Not everything in Bramble is exactly how it seems - in this strange land with creatures big and small, you must be careful when to approach and when to hide. Many hungry and spiteful beasts lurk in these forests and caves. Watch your step....</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1623940/extras/BrambleTMK_RunningGnomes.gif?t=1730299925\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1623940/extras/a_LIGHT.png?t=1730299925\" />Call upon the Spark of Courage, an enchanted fragment granting the gifts you need to endure the pitfalls and trials in your path. Defeat the horrid creatures you encounter in different and unique ways. Be warned, courage without kindness can take you down a dark path.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1623940/extras/Spark_of_Courage.gif?t=1730299925\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1623940/extras/Key_Features.png?t=1730299925\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Adventure as Olle, a brave boy who sets off to rescue his sister. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> A beautiful yet dangerous world to explore. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Encounter twisted, mythical creatures from Nordic folklore for epic-scale boss battles. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Tense, heart-pounding moments with hi-end visuals to match. </p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Butcher","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1623940/77c6b3f9f6a669d30e2ef003c8ad8b0e6691585d.jpg"},{"name":"N\u00e4cken","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1623940/57dcf91b50f2381f2b7317316bb24c1fe1f8681f.jpg"},{"name":"K\u00e4rrh\u00e4xan","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1623940/8f2d9c2732f2e176074fdb7e0a5e59861f666539.jpg"},{"name":"Skogsr\u00e5et","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1623940/622ab9dba0cf7d14d7e0db2b8bf2b18d02730f38.jpg"},{"name":"Pesta","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1623940/ec8d91927a898349983be70dbc973ce5c6abe1e8.jpg"},{"name":"Bramble","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1623940/da137c7c0244a415e11204d79b550ca13453b9f6.jpg"},{"name":"The Mountain King","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1623940/7285e0ffa5b1dde42e476a6eceef55c9574ee170.jpg"},{"name":"Home Again","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1623940/9e50f361dccd593ef18583f2ce3b4cc3a49d4bad.jpg"},{"name":"Bouncy","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1623940/7c275163fab374c47b955dd09481db0479e4ed89.jpg"},{"name":"Collector","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1623940/11f